# 🎥 YouTube Clone UI/UX Design

Welcome to the **YouTube Clone UI/UX Design** project! This repository showcases a front-end design concept inspired by YouTube, with a focus on an intuitive user experience and visually appealing user interface.

![YouTube Clone Preview](link-to-image)  <!-- Replace with actual image link or remove -->

## 🚀 Project Overview

This project is a prototype for a **YouTube-like video streaming platform** designed for educational purposes. The goal is to mimic the basic features of YouTube while implementing custom UI and UX improvements for a seamless user experience.

### Features:
- 🖥️ **Homepage**: Display trending and recommended videos.
- 🎥 **Video Player Page**: View videos with a clean player UI.
- 🔍 **Search Functionality**: A design for the video search bar and results page.
- 📄 **Video Details**: Title, description, and comments section UI.
- 👤 **User Profile**: A simple user account and profile design.

